snippet.title: Rhythm Towers: Gameplay Preview Trailer [4k/60]
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://s.team/a/1561030


Rhythm Towers is a new and unique rhythm based tower defense game. 
Taking place on a distant alien planet, players must use their rhythm matching skills to build up defensive towers in order to fight back mysterious hordes of creatures that will stop at nothing, to destroy the planet's rhythm core. 
Playable solo or jam with a friend through couch/online co-op.

Website: https://rhythmtowers.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/8YDxytt
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rhythmtowers
